[0.005, "o", "\u001b[3m                                        Guided Onboarding Topics                                         \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m┃\u001b[0m\u001b[1m \u001b[0m\u001b[1mTopic             \u001b[0m\u001b[1m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m┃\u001b[0m\u001b[1m \u001b[0m\u001b[1mDescription                                                                     \u001b[0m\u001b[1m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m┃\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m┡━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━╇━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┩\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36mwelcome           \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36"]
[0.000, "o", "m│\u001b[0m Welcome me to openSUSE and give me a brief overview of what makes it special.    \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36mpackage_management\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m Explain how package management works in openSUSE with zypper. Show me the most c \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36myast              \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m What is YaST and how do I use it for system administration?                      \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36mrepositories      \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m How do repositories work in openSUSE? How do I add, remove, and manage them?     \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36mdesktop           \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m Guide me through customizing my desktop environment on openSUSE.                 \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36mfirewall          \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m How do I configure the firewall on openSUSE?                                     \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36mupdates           \u001b[0m\u001b["]
[0.000, "o", "1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m How do I keep my openSUSE system up to date? Explain the update process.         \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36mtroubleshooting   \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m What are common troubleshooting steps when something goes wrong on openSUSE?     \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36mcommunity         \u001b[0m\u001b[1;36m \u001b[0m\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m Tell me about the openSUSE community and how I can get involved.                 \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m└────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2mUse: topic \u001b[0m\u001b[1;2m<\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2;95mname\u001b[0m\u001b[1;2m>\u001b[0m\u001b[2m — e.g. \u001b[0m\u001b[2;32m'topic package_management'\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
